    "comment": "Rationale: Enhanced synapse formation by overexpression of PTPRT.\nLoss of synapses by knockdown of PTPRT.\nKnockdown of PTPRT in cultured neurons (DIV 13-16) decreased the frequency, but not amplitude of mEPSCs.. Experimental description: Materials and methods\nCell culture and transfection\nPrimary hippocampal neuronal cultures were as described earlier (Lee et al, 2003)\nNeuron Culture, Transfection, and Immunostaining-Primary hippocampal neuronal cultures were prepared from rat embryonic brain (embryonic day 18)\n\nDNA constructs\nFull-length human PTPRT (NM_133170, aa 1-1460; from a human brain cDNA library; Clontech) was subcloned into GW1-CMV.",
